PrecisOrder authorizing the trip to Cambodia undertaken by two Members of Parliament, Mr. W.L.R. (LEE) CLARK (Brandon-Souris) and Mr. JESSE P. FLIS (Parkdale-High Park), from May 18 to May 30, 1993, in order to observe the democratic aspects of the elections organized by the United Nations.
